headline: National Duals Invitational Partners With FloSports and ESPN to Deliver Every Match Live
summary: OKLAHOMA CITY, October 06, 2025--The National Duals Invitational, a groundbreaking $1 million collegiate wrestling event sponsored by Paycom, has announced broadcast partnerships with FloSports and ESPN. All 28 duals will be carried live, giving fans nationwide access to every moment of the high-stakes tournament.

headline: 2 of Wall Street’s Favorite Stocks on Our Watchlist and 1 That Underwhelm
summary: The stocks in this article have caught Wall Street’s attention in a big way, with price targets implying returns above 20%. But investors should take these forecasts with a grain of salt because analysts typically say nice things about companies so their firms can win business in other product lines like M&A advisory.
